{
  "stem": "5639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got out of Auschwitz because my girlfriend, obviously, was not as deeply shocked as I was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was shocked into a state of a complete inertia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said-- you see when we were entering Auschwitz through that infamous gate-- Arbeit macht frei-- I was on the left side, on the edge of the left side.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the gate stood a guard, a German guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they all urged you to go quick, quick, fast, fast, schnell, schnell, [GERMAN], and the shrieks, and the tempo, and the reality of the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this guard was standing, and as I was passing he said to me in German, to Auschwitz you enter through the gate and out you go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he jerked his head towards the smoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we were running, and we were running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I really thought that we are in an asylum, in a huge asylum, that they put us in an asylum.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, at one stage they-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then something very unusual happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Eventually from all big groups, small groups emerge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In every big group, you don't stay in a big group, you- you form a tighter group.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A smaller group.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people with whom we were in Annaburg, we kept together, few people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly a German in a striped uniform with a red triangle-- I didn't know what that means, none of it-- approached me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we were perhaps ten girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I said we still looked very human.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he addressed me in a beautiful, elegant German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I answered him in an equally elegant and correct and educated German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he engaged me in a conversation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, is there anything that you would like to know?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
